    • Method Detail

      • scan

        public void scan(IOsmonautReceiver receiver)
        Starts the scanning process.
        Parameters:

      • setWayNodeTags

        public void setWayNodeTags(boolean wayNodeTags)
        Parameters:
        wayNodeTags - Whether way-nodes should have tags. Disabling lowers memory usage. Defaults to 'true'.

      • setProcessors

        public void setProcessors(int processors)
        Parameters:
        processors - Number of processors to use to decode the pbf. By default all available processors are used.

      • setStoreOnDisk

        public void setStoreOnDisk(boolean storeOnDisk)
        Parameters:
        storeOnDisk - Whether entity caches should be stored on disk. Enabling this leads to lower memory usage but takes more time. Defaults to 'false'.

      • setVerbosity

        public void setVerbosity(int verbosity)
        Parameters:
        verbosity - Sets the verbosity level. The levels are: *0: Prints only errors *1: Prints also the most important progress steps
